data.title: Roberts Pizzarotti Pty: Revenue, Competitors, Alternatives
data.meta_description: Roberts Pizzarotti Pty top competitors are Bouygues Construction Australia, INTREC and Roberts Pizzarotti Pty and they have annual revenue of $188.5M  and 520  employees.
data.text:
Roberts Pizzarotti is an Australian construction company, jointly owned by Andrew Roberts, and one of Europe's leading construction and Infrastructure firms, Impresa Pizzarotti & C. S.p.A. The deal marks the first entry into the Australian market for Pizzarotti, which was founded in 1910 in Parma, Italy and now operates in more than seventeen countries across North America, Europe, Africa and the Middle East. Led by chief executive officer Alison Mirams, Roberts Pizzarotti brings together a team with unsurpassed local knowledge and the strength of a large scale, international tier one construction and infrastructure firm. www.robertspizzarotti.com
